release_note: Version 3.0.1 with many new features. Fix the error of increasing or decreasing the volume of background music and vocals Return echo 2 like the old version Fix other errors

Add top page Allows listening to recordings in background music mode Change the community page interface Upgraded recording feature allowing you to undo to record again Supports adjusting music tone and increasing or decreasing background music Support for adding image libraries Allows you to choose cover photos and image slides Added recording playlist
Fix zalo login error Remove the function to buy Mic and Recording features and make all features free. Allows sharing personal songs on social networks. Fix other errors.
Fix video not expanding to full screen when in fullscreen mode and other errors
Upgraded community search and song search. Added chat with Kekara

Fixed the error of echo automatically returning to default when opening the mic. Fixed an error where writing a long comment could not be sent in the theater room. Added Kekara notification filtering. fix other errors.
Fixed an issue where the mic sound was hissing when starting to record and when singing live. Other bug fixes.
Fixed the error of sound noise when starting to sing live in the theater room. Upgrade allows selecting multiple sound effects in the microphone screen. Fix other errors.

Supports logging in with Apple account Fix the error of automatically logging out the app when shutting down the app Fix video playback error that often freezes Improved loading speed for solo and duet songs in the theater room Fix song download error that always fails.
Fix video playback error that often freezes Fix app crash error when playing the next song Improved song loading when singing live in the theater room Supports logging in with Apple account

Fixed the error of singing a duet with the 1st verse without hearing the 1st verse in the singing room Add gift giving feature to the person who sings the 1st verse in the theater room Fixed the error of video freezing when passing the lesson Fix other errors
Increase video loading speed in live rooms Fixed an error where the song could not be live Fix other errors. Fix crash app.

Added Kekara Live room theater feature. Fixed an error where vocal adjustment was misaligned after recording. Online storage of favorites list. Reduce storage capacity when recording songs. Fix other errors. Fix crash app.

Add duet function Add gift giving feature Increase the speed of uploading recordings to the community Increase video loading speed Allow updating background images on personal pages Allow deleting all notifications
